These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, spanish
2 different games are played: go, whist
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
1. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the british is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Nationality      | spanish     | british      |
| Game          | whist | go    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Transport   | van  | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, emerald
2 different games are played: snooker, billiard
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who likes emerald##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | goldfish        | lizard    |
| Color       | brown         | emerald |
| Game         | billiard | snooker   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, bellflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, coach
There 2 different types of food: apple, cabbage
1. the dancer is in an odd position##4
2. the coach is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
3. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Flower   | tulip       | bellflower    |
| Job   | dancer | coach |
| Food           | apple        | cabbage   |

