.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cherry, asparagus
2 different pets are kept: bird, mouse
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
2. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food         | asparagus | cherry  |
| Pet           | mouse  | bird |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Sport     | volleyball   | surfing |

