.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
There are 2 different nationalities: french, japanese
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the french##8
3. the french is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | coffee | 7up |
| Nationality   | japanese    | french     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing  | hiking    |
| Music-Genre     | d&b     | trance       |

